---
const M = '/assets/media/projects/web-dev/tranche-de-cake';
---

<section class="tdc-project relative container mx-auto flex flex-col gap-4 px-4 py-4">
  <div class="project-summary-card tdc-card">
    <div class="tdc-card-inner flex flex-col gap-4">
      <h2 class="font-display m-0 text-4xl uppercase">Tranche de CaKe</h2>

      <div class="tdc-copy">
        <p>
          For this e-commerce project, I collaborated with Belgian founders, Arnaud and Virginie, to
          create an online platform that offers a diverse range of handcrafted snacks delivered
          directly to customers' doors. The site features a minimalist design aesthetic with an earthy
          color palette of terracotta, orange, and chocolate brown that enhances the artisanal feel of
          the products. I focused on a simple, intuitive interface that reflects the homemade nature of
          the offer. Through this platform, Tranche de CaKe delivers convenience, variety, and the
          richness of authentic, homemade snacks to a broad audience.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between">
        <div class="md:w-8/12">
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl tracking-wide uppercase">Responsibilities</h2>
          <p class="tdc-copy">Web design personalization, Shopify setup, site development and features personalization, website launch.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-4/12 md:pl-10">
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl tracking-wide uppercase">URL</h2>
          <a href="https://tranchedecake.be/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="tdc-copy text-inherit">tranchedecake.be</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mockup-container"><img src={`${M}/mockup-tdc-desktop1-960.avif`} class="mockup1" alt="Tranche de CaKe desktop view 1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
  <div class="mockup-container"><img src={`${M}/mockup-tdc-desktop5-960.avif`} class="mockup2" alt="Tranche de CaKe desktop view 2" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
  <div class="mockup-container"><img src={`${M}/mockup-tdc-phone1-960.avif`} class="mockup3" alt="Tranche de CaKe mobile view" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>

  <div class="cards-container flex flex-col gap-4">
    <div class="video-intro">
      <div class="project-card project-card-video">
        <video class="video-projet" src="/media/videos/video-tdc-accueil.mp4" poster={`${M}/tdc-desktop1-960.avif`} autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="auto"></video>
      </div>
      <p>Tranche de CaKe,<br />la révolution de la collation</p>
    </div>

    <div class="project-card"><img src={`${M}/tdc-desktop5-960.avif`} class="video-placeholder" alt="Tranche de CaKe desktop view" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
    <div class="project-card"><img src={`${M}/tdc-desktop2-960.avif`} class="video-placeholder" alt="Tranche de CaKe desktop view" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>

    <div class="left">
      <div class="project-card"><img src={`${M}/tdc-desktop3-960.avif`} class="video-placeholder" alt="Tranche de CaKe desktop view" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
      <p>
        The website features an intuitive and user-friendly interface for customizing weekly snack
        boxes, allowing customers to select from a curated range of artisanal snacks to fill their box.
        To ensure a full and satisfying experience, each box must contain exactly 10 snacks before the
        purchase option becomes available.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="right">
      <p>
        This design choice not only enhances user engagement by encouraging exploration of different
        snacks but also minimizes order errors, ensuring that every box ordered meets the startup's
        quality standards. This personalized approach to ordering allows users to tailor their weekly
        deliveries to their specific tastes, making each delivery a unique culinary adventure.
      </p>
      <div class="project-card"><img src={`${M}/tdc-desktop4-960.avif`} class="video-placeholder" alt="Tranche de CaKe desktop view" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
    </div>

    <p class="tdc-bo">
      The Tranche de Cake ecommerce website includes a fully integrated backoffice system designed to
      streamline operations and enhance management efficiency for our client. This backoffice suite
      provides robust tools for order processing, inventory management, and customer relations. It
      allows for real-time tracking of sales trends and inventory levels, ensuring that our client can
      make informed decisions quickly. Additionally, the system supports promotional and marketing
      activities, enabling personalized customer engagements and targeted campaigns. This comprehensive
      backoffice solution empowers our client to maintain a high level of service quality while
      optimizing operational workflows.
    </p>

    <div class="project-card carte">
      <div class="line">
        <div class="image12">
          <div class="photo"><img src={`${M}/tdc-phone2-960.avif`} alt="Tranche de CaKe mobile view" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
          <div class="photo"><img src={`${M}/tdc-phone5-960.avif`} alt="Tranche de CaKe mobile view" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
        </div>
        <div class="image34">
          <div class="photo"><img src={`${M}/tdc-phone4-960.avif`} alt="Tranche de CaKe mobile view" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
          <div class="photo"><img src={`${M}/tdc-phone6-960.avif`} alt="Tranche de CaKe mobile view" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .tdc-card {
    border-radius: var(--project-card-radius);
  }
  .tdc-card-inner {
    padding: 1rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .tdc-card-inner {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
  .tdc-card h2 {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  .tdc-copy {
    font-family: 'Red Hat Text', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .tdc-bo {
    color: var(--interactive-primary);
  }

  .video-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top;
    border-radius: var(--project-card-radius);
  }
  .mockup-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .mockup1 {
    width: 55%;
  }
  .mockup2 {
    width: 45%;
  }
  .mockup3 {
    width: 65%;
  }
  .mockup1,
  .mockup2,
  .mockup3 {
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top;
    border-radius: var(--project-card-radius);
  }
  .project-card {
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 15px;
    border-radius: var(--project-card-radius);
  }
  .project-card img,
  .video-projet {
    border: 2px var(--surface-muted) solid;
  }
  .project-card-video {
    width: 63%;
  }
  .video-projet {
    overflow: hidden;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top;
    border-radius: var(--project-card-radius);
  }
  .video-intro {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .video-intro p {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    width: 37%;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-family: var(--font-family-display);
    line-height: 1.9167rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 23px;
    color: var(--interactive-primary);
  }
  .left,
  .right {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .left {
    justify-content: left;
  }
  .right {
    justify-content: right;
  }
  .left > .project-card,
  .right > .project-card {
    width: 70%;
  }
  .left p,
  .right p {
    width: 30%;
    color: var(--interactive-primary);
  }
  .right p {
    text-align: right;
  }
  .project-card.carte {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 624px;
    padding: 15px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .line {
    display: flex;
    gap: 15px;
    height: 100%;
  }
  .image12,
  .image34 {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    gap: 15px;
    flex: 1;
    height: 100%;
  }
  .image12 .photo,
  .image34 .photo {
    flex: 1;
    overflow: hidden;
    height: 100%;
  }
  .image12 .photo img,
  .image34 .photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top;
  }
  .photo img {
    border-radius: var(--project-card-radius);
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 970px) {
    .video-intro {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .video-intro p,
    .project-card-video {
      width: 100%;
    }
    .mockup1,
    .mockup2,
    .mockup3 {
      width: 90%;
    }
    .project-card.carte {
      height: 420px;
    }
  }
  @media screen and (max-width: 628px) {
    .left,
    .right {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .left > .project-card,
    .right > .project-card,
    .left p,
    .right p {
      width: unset;
    }
    .left > .project-card {
      order: 2;
    }
    .right p {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>
